            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I haven't found anywhere where I think we want anything other than a callback/`map`.\r\n\r\nThe only place I can think of would be potentially in `triggerCharacters` for completion. An LSP could theoretically register multiple times with different triggers.",
